item.title: Contact C-MOOR
item.description: Send us an e-mail at c-moor@carnegiescience.edu Chat with us on Slack (e-mail us for an invitation) Other Resources You can find links for learning more about a variety of topics on our Resources page (Learn > Resources) You can find cheat sheets for common commands on our Cheat Sheets page (Learn > Cheat Sheets) You can often find helpful discussions by searching the internet. Try copying your code or error message into your preferred search engine, and you will usually find other people with the same problem and one or more solutions.
